Package: fiducia.client
Type: Package
Title: Fiducia HTTP Client for fiducia.cloud
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("fiducia.cloud", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "clients@fiducia.cloud")
Maintainer: fiducia.cloud <clients@fiducia.cloud>
Description: A dependency-light client for the fiducia.cloud HTTP API,
    covering distributed locks, semaphores, reader-writer locks, idempotency
    keys, a configuration key-value store, rate limiting, cron scheduling,
    leader election and service discovery over one shared HTTP contract.
License: file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports: httr, jsonlite, utils
URL: https://github.com/fiducia-cloud/fiducia-clients
BugReports: https://github.com/fiducia-cloud/fiducia-clients/issues
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
